sequenceDiagram
    participant G as Go gRPC SDK
    participant P as Proxy :8081
    participant N as NameServer :9876
    participant B as Broker :10911

    G->>P: QueryRoute / Telemetry
    P->>N: 查询 Topic 路由
    N-->>P: Broker 与队列信息
    P-->>G: 返回 gRPC 路由结果
    G->>P: SendMessage
    P->>B: 写入消息
    B-->>P: SendResult
    P-->>G: SendReceipt
